D. Jarjabek, poslanec: }{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
\u270\'0eakujem ve\u318\'3emi pekne za slovo, p\u225\'e1n predsedaj\u250\'faci. Ja budem ve\u318\'3emi stru\u269\'0dn\u253\'fd. Len som chcel poveda\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee obdivujem va\u353\'61u trpezlivos\u357\'65, p\u225\'e1n podpredseda vl\u225\'e1dy, a to dr\u382\'7eanie sa hesla: Kto do teba kame\u328\'48om, ty do\u328\'48ho chlebom. Len sa ob\u225\'e1vam, \u382\'7ee toho chleba bude e\u353\'61te treba ve\u318\'3ea vyh\u225\'e1dza\u357\'65. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
\u270\'0eakujem za pozornos\u357\'65.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6

