Bod 6: \u8222\'1eAby zradcovia slovensk\u233\'e9ho n\u225\'e1roda, ktor\u237\'ed svoju materinsk\u250\'fa re\u269\'0d potupuj\u250\'fa, nesmeli medzi Slov\u225\'e1kmi \u250\'faradova\u357\'65.\u8220\'1c Nu\u382\'7e, asi na\u353\'61e rady by boli o m\u225\'e1linko prerieden\u233\'e9.  }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
