\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
V s\u250\'falade s rozhodnut\u237\'edm predsedu N\u225\'e1rodnej rady z 27. marca navrhujem, aby z\u225\'e1kon prerokovali nasleduj\u250\'face v\u253\'fdbory: \u250\'fastavnopr\u225\'e1vny v\u253\'fdbor, v\u253\'fdbor pre financie, rozpo\u269\'0det a menu, v\u253\'fdbor pre \u318\'3eudsk\u233\'e9 pr\u225\'e1va, n\u225\'e1rodnosti a postavenie \u382\'7eien a v\u253\'fdbor pre kult\u250\'faru a m\u233\'e9di\u225\'e1. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
