Dovo\u318\'3ete mi aspo\u328\'48 p\u225\'e1r pozn\u225\'e1mok k niektor\u253\'fdm rie\u353\'61en\u253\'fdm okruhom, ktor\u233\'e9 s\u250\'fa uv\u225\'e1dzan\u233\'e9. Spomeniem, \u382\'7ee jedn\u253\'fdm z nich je napr\u237\'edklad vyu\u382\'7eitie \u250\'fazemia, ochrana d\u244\'f4le\u382\'7eit\u253\'fdch z\u225\'e1ujmov \u250\'fazem\u237\'ed na z\u225\'e1klade \u250\'fazemn\u233\'e9ho pl\u225\'e1nu. Je to, samozrejme, vec, ktor\u225\'e1 by mala by\u357\'65 na\u353\'61\u237\'edm hlavn\u253\'fdm z\u225\'e1ujmom. Na druhej strane s t\u253\'fdm koliduj\u250\'fa aj ur\u269\'0dit\u233\'e9 \u271\'0fal\u353\'61ie okruhy, ktor\u233\'e9 s\u250\'fa u\u382\'7e viac probl\u233\'e9mov\u233\'e9, a to je napr\u237\'edklad vymedzovanie ur\u269\'0dit\u253\'fdch podmienok, ktor\u233\'e9 nahr\u225\'e1dzaj\u250\'fa \u250\'fazemn\u233\'e9 rozhodnutia pri zon\u225\'e1lnych pl\u225\'e1noch alebo pri niektor\u253\'fdch stavb\u225\'e1ch, ktor\u233\'e9 nevy\u382\'7eaduj\u250\'fa ohl\u225\'e1senie, aj napriek dobr\u233\'e9mu \u250\'famyslu v\u253\'fdrazne zr\u253\'fdchli\u357\'65 povo\u318\'3eovacie procesy alebo zefekt\u237\'edvni\u357\'65 v\u253\'fdkon \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tneho doh\u318\'3eadu. Tie\u382\'7e s\u250\'fa tam mo\u382\'7en\u233\'e9 probl\u233\'e9my v bud\u250\'facnosti pri danom n\u225\'e1vrhu ustanoven\u237\'ed z\u225\'e1kona. Toti\u382\'7e nie v\u353\'61etky zjednodu\u353\'61enia n\u225\'e1m prines\u250\'fa iba klady, ale prines\u250\'fa n\u225\'e1m aj probl\u233\'e9my. Typick\u253\'fdm probl\u233\'e9mov\u253\'fdm bodom je napr\u237\'edklad probl\u233\'e9m zastavenia stavebn\u253\'fdch pr\u225\'e1c vo\u269\'0di stavebn\u237\'edkovi, zhotovite\u318\'3eovi a dod\u225\'e1vate\u318\'3eovi. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Mo\u382\'7eno teda o\u269\'0dak\u225\'e1va\u357\'65 r\u244\'f4zne probl\u233\'e9my a tieto probl\u233\'e9my bud\u250\'fa z v\u228\'e4\u269\'0d\u353\'61ej \u269\'0dasti predov\u353\'61etk\u253\'fdm na pleciach obc\u237\'ed a miest. A ke\u271\'0f\u382\'7ee nie je jednoduch\u233\'e9 zabezpe\u269\'0di\u357\'65 dobr\u253\'fd v\u253\'fdkon tohto z\u225\'e1kona a ke\u271\'0f\u382\'7ee chceme, aby aj obce a mest\u225\'e1 mali pri uplat\u328\'48ovan\u237\'ed tohto z\u225\'e1kona \u269\'0do najlep\u353\'61ie podmienky, tak si mysl\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee je potrebn\u233\'e9 aj pripravi\u357\'65 dobr\u253\'fd n\u225\'e1vrh tohto z\u225\'e1kona.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Ur\u269\'0dite pre v\u353\'61etk\u253\'fdch z n\u225\'e1s by malo by\u357\'65 spolo\u269\'0dn\u253\'fdm z\u225\'e1ujmom zabezpe\u269\'0denie kvality vykon\u225\'e1vanej \u269\'0dinnosti, \u269\'0di u\u382\'7e stavebn\u253\'fdch \u250\'faradov, ako aj prenesen\u233\'e9ho v\u253\'fdkonu \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tnej spr\u225\'e1vy, ale aj samotnej pr\u237\'edpravy kvalitn\u233\'e9ho n\u225\'e1vrhu stavebn\u233\'e9ho z\u225\'e1kona, a preto mi dovo\u318\'3ete upozorni\u357\'65 na niektor\u233\'e9 ustanovenia z\u225\'e1kona, ktor\u233\'e9 n\u225\'e1m tieto probl\u233\'e9my m\u244\'f4\u382\'7eu sp\u244\'f4sobi\u357\'65. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
A teraz u\u382\'7e konkr\u233\'e9tne k niektor\u253\'fdm ustanoveniam.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Ak za\u269\'0dnem tu, kde sme, teda v Bratislave, tak samotn\u233\'e9 mesto Bratislava ur\u269\'0dite bude ma\u357\'65 so spom\u237\'ednan\u253\'fdm nov\u253\'fdm z\u225\'e1konom probl\u233\'e9my, ke\u271\'0f\u382\'7ee spom\u237\'ednan\u253\'fdm n\u225\'e1vrhom z\u225\'e1kona, teda novelou z\u225\'e1kona o\~Bratislave, pardon, ke\u271\'0f\u382\'7ee novelou z\u225\'e1kona o Bratislave bol doplnen\u253\'fd \u167\'a7 1 ods. 2, pod\u318\'3ea ktor\u233\'e9ho mestsk\u225\'e1 \u269\'0das\u357\'65 vykon\u225\'e1va samospr\u225\'e1vu Bratislavy a prenesen\u250\'fa p\u244\'f4sobnos\u357\'65 v rozsahu vymedzenom z\u225\'e1konom a \u353\'61tat\u250\'fatom Bratislavy a v tomto rozsahu m\u225\'e1 postavenie obce. Platn\u253\'fd stavebn\u253\'fd z\u225\'e1kon s\u237\'edce stanovuje, \u382\'7ee \u250\'fa\u269\'0dastn\u237\'edk konania je obec, ak nie je stavebn\u253\'fdm \u250\'faradom pr\u237\'edslu\u353\'61n\u253\'fdm pre \u250\'fazemn\u233\'e9 konanie. Ale v n\u225\'e1vrhu z\u225\'e1kona s\u250\'fa ustanovenia, ktor\u233\'e9 bud\u250\'fa asi sp\u244\'f4sobova\u357\'65 probl\u233\'e9my. Je to \u167\'a7 79 ods. 1 p\u237\'edsm. n) a \u167\'a7 122 ods. 2. Cez tieto ustanovenia, ktor\u233\'e9 v podstate vymedzuj\u250\'fa postavenie obce, nebudem ich teraz \u269\'0d\u237\'edta\u357\'65, uviedol som paragrafy, tak z toho celkovo vypl\u253\'fdva, \u382\'7ee Bratislava asi bude ma\u357\'65 probl\u233\'e9m s t\u253\'fdm, \u382\'7ee na konkr\u233\'e9tnom \u250\'fazem\u237\'ed bud\u250\'fa vymedzen\u233\'e9 dve obce. Okrem mesta, ktor\u233\'e9 je obcou a nie je stavebn\u253\'fdm \u250\'faradom, aj \u271\'0fal\u353\'61ia obec, pr\u237\'edslu\u353\'61n\u225\'e1 mestsk\u225\'e1 \u269\'0das\u357\'65, ktor\u225\'e1 je obcou a stavebn\u253\'fdm \u250\'faradom pr\u237\'edslu\u353\'61n\u253\'fdm pre \u250\'fazemn\u233\'e9 konanie. To je prv\u253\'fd probl\u233\'e9m. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
V \u167\'a7 17 ods. 3, \u167\'a7 18 ods. 2, kde sa uklad\u225\'e1 povinnos\u357\'65 pre spr\u225\'e1vcov siet\u237\'ed vies\u357\'65 dokument\u225\'e1ciu a s\u250\'favisiace veci, nechcem to teraz tu podrobnej\u353\'61ie rozv\u225\'e1dza\u357\'65, tak bude napr\u237\'edklad probl\u233\'e9m v bud\u250\'facnosti s t\u253\'fdm, ako sa bud\u250\'fa v praxi aplikova\u357\'65 \u250\'fahrady za tieto inform\u225\'e1cie, ke\u271\'0f\u382\'7ee to nie je jednozna\u269\'0dne definovan\u233\'e9. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
V \u167\'a7 19 je upraven\u253\'fd in\u353\'61tit\u250\'fat \u250\'fazemnopl\u225\'e1novanej inform\u225\'e1cie. Na druhej strane op\u228\'e4\u357\'65 tam absentuje, ako sa bude rie\u353\'61i\u357\'65 \u353\'61koda. Je tam s\u237\'edce stanoven\u233\'e9, \u382\'7ee org\u225\'e1n, ktor\u253\'fd \u250\'fazemnopl\u225\'e1novaciu inform\u225\'e1ciu vydal, zn\u225\'e1\u353\'61a \u353\'61kodu, ale to ustanovenie je ve\u318\'3emi v\u353\'61eobecn\u233\'e9 z h\u318\'3eadiska definovania pojmu \u353\'61kody a nespr\u225\'e1vnych \u250\'fadajov, ako aj ich vz\u225\'e1jomnej podmienenosti. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
V \u271\'0fal\u353\'61\u237\'edch paragrafoch 43, 58, 52 predkladate\u318\'3e navrhuje, \u382\'7ee obec sa bude musie\u357\'65 zaobera\u357\'65 r\u244\'f4znymi n\u225\'e1vrhmi na zmeny, ktor\u233\'e9 bude musie\u357\'65 posudzova\u357\'65, \u269\'0di maj\u250\'fa n\u225\'e1le\u382\'7eitosti a potom rozhodova\u357\'65, \u269\'0di bude obstar\u225\'e1va\u357\'65 \u250\'fazemn\u253\'fd pl\u225\'e1n, resp. jeho zmeny. Nie je v\u353\'61ak u\u382\'7e potom celkom jasn\u233\'e9, kto rozhodne, \u269\'0di je potrebn\u233\'e9 obstara\u357\'65 tieto zmeny a doplnky, o ktor\u253\'fdch obec mus\u237\'ed zase bezodkladne a p\u237\'edsomne upovedomi\u357\'65 navrhovate\u318\'3ea. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
\u270\'0eal\u353\'61\u237\'ed, mo\u382\'7eno jeden z t\u253\'fdch najv\u225\'e1\u382\'7enej\u353\'61\u237\'edch probl\u233\'e9mov, je aj probl\u233\'e9m, ktor\u253\'fd sa t\u253\'fdka \u167\'a7 46 ods. 5 a je to zabezpe\u269\'0denie bud\u250\'faceho vyu\u382\'7eitia \u250\'fazemia pod\u318\'3ea pripravovan\u233\'e9ho \u250\'fazemn\u233\'e9ho pl\u225\'e1nu obce. Najnesk\u244\'f4r pred za\u269\'0dat\u237\'edm prerokovania n\u225\'e1vrhu \u250\'fazemn\u233\'e9ho pl\u225\'e1nu obce m\u225\'e1 poda\u357\'65 n\u225\'e1vrh na za\u269\'0datie konania o stavebnej uz\u225\'e1vere. Formul\u225\'e1cia v\u353\'61ak pod\u318\'3ea n\u225\'e1zoru t\u253\'fdch, ktor\u237\'ed sa tejto problematike venuj\u250\'fa, prakticky znemo\u382\'7en\u237\'ed vyd\u225\'e1vanie rozhodnutia o stavebnej uz\u225\'e1vere pri \u250\'fazemnom pl\u225\'e1ne hlavn\u233\'e9ho mesta. No ale mysl\u237\'edm si, \u382\'7ee tento z\u225\'e1kon neplat\u237\'ed len pre Bratislavu. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Tak\u382\'7ee, po\u271\'0fme aj k \u271\'0fal\u353\'61\u237\'edm paragrafom, ktor\u233\'e9 sp\u244\'f4sobia probl\u233\'e9my nielen v\~Bratislave, ale aj ostatn\u253\'fdm obciam a mest\u225\'e1m. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
V \u167\'a7 80 ods. 2 \u269\'0di v \u167\'a7 123 ods. 3 p\u237\'edsm. a) a \u167\'a7 125 ods. 5 p\u237\'edsm. b) sa \u382\'7eiada spresni\u357\'65 sp\u244\'f4sob preukazovania vz\u357\'65ahu k pozemku, na ktorom m\u225\'e1 by\u357\'65 stavba umiestnen\u225\'e1 s cie\u318\'3eom pred\u237\'eds\u357\'65 r\u244\'f4znym interpret\u225\'e1ci\u225\'e1m a r\u244\'f4znorodej aplik\u225\'e1cii v praxi. Pr\u225\'e1ve tak\u233\'e9to nejasne zadefinovan\u233\'e9 veci ve\u318\'3emi \u269\'0dasto sp\u244\'f4sobuj\u250\'fa pri uveden\u237\'ed z\u225\'e1kona do \u382\'7eivota probl\u233\'e9my.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
